ch.bfh.ti.sed.patmon1.server.controller

Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.ti.sed.patmon1.server.controller.Session

  • public class Session
extends Object
    A Session is used to store an authenticated doctor session it the SessionStorage. It is handed over to the client and the client has to authenticate each request using it's session.

    There is no interface for this class since JAX-WS does not support interfaces to be sent over to the client.
